  <!-- Basic info -->
  <name>ProPadp</name>
  <summary>A modern text editor with rich formatting</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      My GTK App is a modern, user-friendly text editor built with GTK 4 and Libadwaita.
      It provides a clean interface for writing and editing documents with rich formatting capabilities.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clean and intuitive interface following GNOME HIG</li>
      <li>Rich text formatting with toolbar</li>
      <li>File manager for organizing documents</li>
      <li>Search and replace functionality</li>
      <li>Export to multiple formats</li>
      <li>Dark mode support</li>
      <li>Auto-save functionality</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Whether you're taking notes, writing documentation, or editing markdown files,
      My GTK App provides all the tools you need in a distraction-free environment.
    </p>
  </description>
  
